    <h1>Inbound Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">A strategy that attracts customers by creating <strong>useful content and experiences</strong> that pull them toward your business — rather than pushing messages out through ads, cold calls, or interruption marketing. Coined by HubSpot in 2006.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
